OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with scattered showers.
OL,6,FThese showers become frequent, heavy
OL,7,Fand blustery with hail and thunder in
OL,8,Fthe west at times from the morning.
OL,9,FThe strong southwest wind will reach
OL,10,Fgale force in places.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FBlustery showers in the west
OL,13,Fand the north will clear during the
OL,14,Fevening. Increasing clear periods and
OL,15,Fwinds falling light bring a patchy
OL,16,Finland frost.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FThe morning will begin mostly
OL,19,Fdry with bright spells. Cloud and
OL,20,Fscattered showers spread north from
OL,21,Fthe late morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
