OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith sunny periods Tuesday morning.
OL,7,FCloud and rain, heavy at times,
OL,8,Fspreads northeast late Tuesday and
OL,9,Fcontinues through Wednesday. The rain
OL,10,Fturns showery during Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
